calvin 's journey is amazing ! okay so calvin is n't the smartest , bravest , coolest kid in his hometown , receda . but after he loses a baseball game for his team the knights he is magically transported back in time to the days of king arthur . a place where is 20th century knowlege and courage is all that can protect him . when he finds out that merlin himself was the one that brought him hear he is shocked ( and so is merlin ) that calvin is supposed to be a hero that will save king arthur 's kingdom . will calivn suceed ? or is he better of in the 20th century . if you like midevil tales and kid flicks you should see this movie . hey , cal is n't that bad looking either =